song_lyrics: Jene bhajane re pāme bhavjaḷ pār... pragaṭ 1
Karuṇānidhi re Prabhu param udār... pragaṭ 2
Vahāle kaḷī madhye ati karuṇā karī,
Dhāryo dvijkuḷ re guṇnidhi avatār... pragaṭ 3
Tāḷyā nij jannā manthī madmār... pragaṭ 4
Te to tari gayā re kuḷ sahit sansār... pragaṭ 5
Kare nishdin re neti nigam pokār... pragaṭ 6
title: Sukhdāyak re Swāmī Sahajānand
